  "Revising a prediction model when new data becomes available or when the underlying conditions change, to maintain accuracy": "",
  "Replacing the model with a completely different one every day": "",
  "Never changing a model once it is built": "",
  "Updating only the intercept": "",
  "Real-world conditions evolve, so models must be re-evaluated and updated to remain relevant.": "",
